title: Fish and Wildlife Convervation Comission Managment Areas, Florida, 2006
name: Fish and Wildlife Convervation Comission Managment Areas, Florida, 2006
description:
Abstract: This GIS data set represents the 2006 Wildlife Management Areas administered by the Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission (FWC), and other associated public use areas. These data are intended as a general reference map only.
Purpose: This GIS data set was created to represent a comprehensive statewide data set of Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission (FWC) Wildlife Management Areas.
Supplemental Information: Prior to July 1, 2004, the Fish and Wildlife Research Institute (FWRI) was known as the Florida Marine Research Institute (FMRI). The institute name has not been changed in historical data sets or references to work completed by the Florida Marine Research Institute. The institute name has been changed in references to ongoing research, new research, and contact information. More information on activities permitted in individual areas can be found from the links on FWC's Web site: http://myfwc.com/recreation/list.html.
